info.name: NtuaFlix
info.description:
Welcome to the Ntuaflix API! Our platform offers a rich repository of multimedia content, enabling users to explore and engage with a diverse range of movies and series. The Ntuaflix API is designed to provide developers with seamless access to our vast collection, allowing for the integration of Ntuaflix's extensive library into your applications, websites, and services.

The Ntuaflix API grants you the ability to search for movies and TV shows, retrieve detailed information about each title, including cast, genre, ratings, and summaries, as well as access user ratings and reviews. Whether you're building an app that recommends personalized content, a website that showcases the latest and greatest in entertainment, or a service that analyses media trends, our API is your gateway to a wealth of multimedia content.
